_Controller_Art18\" />\n    <gateway id=\"Gateway_RestrictionGround_Art18\" name=\"Which Article 18(1) ground for restriction applies?\" type=\"exclusiveGateway\" poolRef=\"Participant_Controller_Art18\" />\n  </gateways>\n  <sequenceFlows>\n    <sequenceFlow id=\"Flow_GatewayAllowedProcessingBasis_To_EndNoPermittedProcessing_Art18\" name=\"No permitted basis\" sourceRef=\"Gateway_AllowedProcessingBasis_Art18\" targetRef=\"EndEvent_NoPermittedProcessing_Art18\" />\n    <sequenceFlow id=\"Flow_GatewayAllowedProcessingBasis_To_TaskProcessByConsent_Art18\" name=\"The data subject consented to the restricted processing\" sourceRef=\"Gateway_AllowedProcessingBasis_Art18\" targetRef=\"Task_ProcessByConsent_Art18\" />\n    <sequenceFlow id=\"Flow_GatewayAllowedProcessingBasis_To_TaskProcessForLegalClaims_Art18\" name=\"Processing is needed for legal claims\" sourceRef=\"Gateway_AllowedProcessingBasis_Art18\" targetRef=\"Task_ProcessForLegalClaims_Art18\" />\n    <sequenceFlow id=\"Flow_GatewayAllowedProcessingBasis_To_TaskProcessForPublicInterest_Art18\" name=\"Processing is needed for important public interest\" sourceRef=\"Gateway_AllowedProcessingBasis_Art18\" targetRef=\"Task_ProcessForPublicInterest_Art18\" />\n    <sequenceFlow id=\"Flow_GatewayAllowedProcessingBasis_To_TaskProcessToProtectRights_Art18\" name=\"Processing is needed to protect the rights of another person\" sourceRef=\"Gateway_AllowedProcessingBasis_Art18\" targetRef=\"Task_ProcessToProtectRights_Art18\" />\n    <sequenceFlow id=\"Flow_GatewayFurtherProcessingNeeded_To_GatewayAllowedProcessingBasis_Art18\" name=\"Yes\" sourceRef=\"Gateway_FurtherProcessingNeeded_Art18\" targetRef=\"Gateway_AllowedProcessingBasis_Art18\" />\n    <sequenceFlow id=\"Flow_GatewayFurtherProcessingNeeded_To_GatewayLiftRestriction_Art18\" name=\"No\" sourceRef=\"Gateway_FurtherProcessingNeeded_Art18\" targetRef=\"Gateway_LiftRestriction_Art18\" />\n    <sequenceFlow id=\"Flow_GatewayJoinGrounds_To_TaskRestrictProcessing_Art1