be without prejudice to Article 17. That right shall not apply to processing necessary for the performance of a task carried out in the public interest or in the exercise of official authority vested in the controller.\n\n4.   The right referred to in paragraph 1 shall not adversely affect the rights and freedoms of others."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>\n<processModel>\n  <pools>\n    <pool id=\"Participant_Controller_Art20\" name=\"Controller\" poolType=\"active\" processRef=\"Process_Controller_Art20\" />\n    <pool id=\"Participant_DataSubject_Art20\" name=\"Data Subject\" poolType=\"passive\" />\n    <pool id=\"Participant_ReceivingController_Art20\" name=\"Receiving Controller\" poolType=\"passive\" />\n  </pools>\n  <lanes />\n  <tasks>\n    <task id=\"ReceiveTask_ReceivePortabilityRequest_Art20\" name=\"Receive portability request\" type=\"receiveTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_Controller_Art20\" />\n    <task id=\"SendTask_ProvidePortableDataToDataSubject_Art20\" name=\"Provide portable data set\" type=\"sendTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_Controller_Art20\" />\n    <task id=\"SendTask_TransmitDataToReceivingController_Art20\" name=\"Transmit portable data to receiving controller\" type=\"sendTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_Controller_Art20\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_PreparePortableDataset_Art20\" name=\"Prepare portable data set\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_Controller_Art20\" />\n  </tasks>\n  <events>\n    <event id=\"EndEvent_NoPortabilityBasis_Art20\" name=\"No portability right arises because the processing is not carried out by automated means\" type=\"endEvent\" poolRef=\"Participant_Controller_Art20\" />\n    <event id=\"EndEvent_NoPortableDataset_Art20\" name=\"No portability right arises because the processing is not based on Article 6(1)(a), Article 9(2)(a), or Article 6(1)(b)\" type=\"endEvent\" poolRef=\"Participant_Controller_Art20\" />\n    <event id=\"EndEvent_NotAutomated_Art20\" name=\"No portabi