to the data subject.\n\n3.   Irrespective of the terms of the arrangement referred to in paragraph 1, the data subject may exercise his or her rights under this Regulation in respect of and against each of the controllers."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>\n<processModel>\n  <pools>\n    <pool id=\"Participant_DataSubject_Art26\" name=\"Data Subject\" poolType=\"passive\" />\n    <pool id=\"Participant_JointControllerA_Art26\" name=\"Joint Controller A\" poolType=\"active\" processRef=\"Process_JointControllerA_Art26\" />\n    <pool id=\"Participant_JointControllerB_Art26\" name=\"Joint Controller B\" poolType=\"passive\" />\n  </pools>\n  <lanes />\n  <tasks>\n    <task id=\"ReceiveTask_ReceiveArrangementInput_Art26\" name=\"Receive arrangement input\" type=\"receiveTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_JointControllerA_Art26\" />\n    <task id=\"ReceiveTask_ReceiveRightsRequestA_Art26\" name=\"Receive rights request\" type=\"receiveTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_JointControllerA_Art26\" />\n    <task id=\"SendTask_CoordinateArrangement_Art26\" name=\"Coordinate arrangement\" type=\"sendTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_JointControllerA_Art26\" />\n    <task id=\"SendTask_MakeEssenceAvailable_Art26\" name=\"Make arrangement essence available\" type=\"sendTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_JointControllerA_Art26\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_AllocateRightsNoticeDuties_Art26\" name=\"Allocate rights and notice duties\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_JointControllerA_Art26\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_ApplyLegalAllocation_Art26\" name=\"Apply legal allocation\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_JointControllerA_Art26\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_DefineResponsibilities_Art26\" name=\"Define responsibilities\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_JointControllerA_Art26\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_DesignateContactPoint_Art26\" name=\"Designate contact point\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_JointControllerA_Art26\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_ReflectRoles_A