ere they are, under paragraphs 2 and 3, responsible for any damage caused by processing, each controller or processor shall be held liable for the entire damage in order to ensure effective compensation of the data subject.\n\n5.   Where a controller or processor has, in accordance with paragraph 4, paid full compensation for the damage suffered, that controller or processor shall be entitled to claim back from the other controllers or processors involved in the same processing that part of the compensation corresponding to their part of responsibility for the damage, in accordance with the conditions set out in paragraph 2.\n\n6.   Court proceedings for exercising the right to receive compensation shall be brought before the courts competent under the law of the Member State referred to in Article 79(2)."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>\n<processModel>\n  <pools>\n    <pool id=\"Participant_Court_Art82\" name=\"Court\" poolType=\"passive\" />\n    <pool id=\"Participant_DamagedPerson_Art82\" name=\"Damaged Person\" poolType=\"passive\" />\n    <pool id=\"Participant_OtherResponsibleParty_Art82\" name=\"Other Responsible Controller or Processor\" poolType=\"passive\" />\n    <pool id=\"Participant_ReceivingParty_Art82\" name=\"Controller or Processor receiving the compensation claim\" poolType=\"active\" processRef=\"Process_ReceivingParty_Art82\" />\n  </pools>\n  <lanes />\n  <tasks>\n    <task id=\"ReceiveTask_ReceiveCompensationClaim_Art82\" name=\"Receive compensation claim\" type=\"receiveTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_ReceivingParty_Art82\" />\n    <task id=\"SendTask_HandleCourtClaim_Art82\" name=\"Handle claim in Article 79(2) court\" type=\"sendTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_ReceivingParty_Art82\" />\n    <task id=\"SendTask_PayCompensation_Art82\" name=\"Pay compensation\" type=\"sendTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_ReceivingParty_Art82\" />\n    <task id=\"SendTask_PayFullCompensation_Art82\" name=\"Pay full compensatio